 <H1>Joining Attributes</H1> 
 <P><UL>
<LI><H2>Useful if there are interactions among attributes
</H2>
</UL><UL>
<LI><H2>Estimates of probabilitiesroblem-
</H2>
<UL>
<LI> Given: Set of       {age, weight, height, shoe-size}
<LI>Find: Attribute      {age, height, weight}
<LI>Such that accuracy of classifier is maximized
</UL></UL><UL>
<LI><H2>Partition Selection Problem-
</H2>
<UL>
<LI> Given: Set of independent      {{age}, {weight}, {height}, {shoe-size}}
<LI>Find: Attribute      {{age, height}, {weight}}
<LI>Such that accuracy of classifier is maximized</UL></UL></P>
